schafts- und Technikforschung (Science and Technology Studies) vor, darunter Handlungsmacht (agency), Quasi-Objekte, Grenzobjekte, technische Objekte, epistemische Dinge, Akteurnetzwerke, heterogene Assoziationen sowie Objektinstitutionen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAgency. 4aAkteur-Netzwerk-Theorie. 4aKognition. 4aKulturtheorie. 4aSozialität. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aTechnik. 4aTechniksoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aActor-network-theory.  aAgency.  aCognition.  aCultural Theory.  aSocial Relations.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology of Technology.  aSociology.  aTechnology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2016z9783110485332oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070099208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839432976zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839432976423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839432976/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-070099-2  PP Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DSWb2016  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016